cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.CY 

This paper discusses recommendation systems using deep learning techniques, which are commonly studied in the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also focuses on generating explanations for the recommendations, which falls under the sub-categories of information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the use of LSTM-based RNN architecture for recommendation and neighbourhood-based scheme for generating explanations may also be relevant to the sub-category of cybernetics (cs.CY).
